title: United Kingdom Imports - Wadding, Felt & Nonwovens, Special Yarns Articles
description: Imports - Wadding, Felt & Nonwovens, Special Yarns Articles in the United Kingdom increased to 60.75 GBP Million in September from 56.24 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Wadding, Felt & Nonwovens, Special Yarns in the United Kingdom averaged 41.39 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 70.40 GBP Million in May of 2022 and a record low of 18.46 GBP Million in December of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Wadding, Felt & Nonwovens, Special Yar.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
